{"content":[{"key":"header","data":{"level":1,"content":"MRI 产品经理之禅"},"common":{}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"TOC / 内容提要","level":3},"common":{}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"<span>Start to learn English</span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"<span>不要给自己设限</span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"<span>第一性原理</span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"<span>学会使用互联网和办公软件</span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"<span>学会结构化写作</span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"<span>活用MRI原理（哲学）学习MRI</span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span>Start to learn English</span>","level":3},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>与许多科学技术一样，如果一开始就加紧英文的学习，长期收益是非常可观的。可能一开始会觉得为难、不习惯，但随着技术学习的深入，你会越来越发现英文学习的重要性</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span>不要给自己设限</span>","level":3},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>你并不能在一开始就知道自己最感兴趣的研究领域和方向，也不知道在 MRI这座知识迷宫里该往哪个方向走。所以不要一开始就给自己处处设限，可以对各方面的知识都保持好奇心</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span>第一性原理</span>","level":3},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>要重视基础学科的学习。限制你最终高度和成就的是数学、物理、计算机、基础医学（解剖、生理、病理、组胚、遗传）这些专业的水平。很多人学习碰到了天花板，都是因为基础学科知识水平的不足。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>举个例子，很多人理解不了 MRI，不是因为不懂量子力学，而是忘掉了三角函数的知识</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span>学会使用互联网和办公软件</span>","level":3},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"ordered","items":[{"content":"<span>自行学习如何连接使用 Google</span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<span>学会使用 chrome 浏览器和安装一些好用的插件</span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<span>必要的办公软件使用知识</span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<span>有余力学会使用 Markdown 语法和 Markdown 编辑器</span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span>学会结构化写作</span>","level":3},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>结构化写作能让你记笔记和写产品文档时思维敏捷、文思泉涌</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span>活用 MRI原理（哲学）学习 MRI</span>","level":3},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"<span>微积分思维：一切大困难，都可以分解为小努力、小尝试、小进步</span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"<span>傅里叶变换的思维：对称性原则，物理学之美</span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><a href=\"https://www.neomatrix.club/00%20Inbox/MRI%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E7%BB%8F%E7%90%86%E4%B9%8B%E7%A6%85\"><span>MRI产品经理之禅</span></a></span><span></span><span>ZEN of a MRI Product Manager</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"level":3,"content":"Bear + Roam, 有没有搞头?"},"common":{}},{"key":"image","data":{"image":{"assetName":"1692602647896-image.png","url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Neonity2020/geekeditor/geekeditor_images/2023-8-21/1692602647896-image.png"},"caption":"「Roam Research」老牌双链大纲笔记，在后起之秀不断横空出世的今天，依旧是标杆级笔记产品","withCaption":true},"common":{}},{"key":"image","data":{"image":{"assetName":"1692600870635-image.png","url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Neonity2020/geekeditor/geekeditor_images/2023-8-21/1692600870635-image.png"},"caption":"「Bear | 熊掌记」是我非常喜欢的一个笔记软件, UI非常漂亮","withCaption":true},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>一直很喜欢<footnote data-note=\"https://roamresearch.com/\" data-title=\"Roam Research笔记\">Roam</footnote>的流畅，也很喜欢<footnote data-note=\"https://bear.app/\" data-title=\"Bear笔记 | 熊掌记\">Bear笔记</footnote>的高颜值。有没有将二者合二为一，完美笔记体验的方法呢？</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>受<footnote data-note=\"玉树芝兰\" data-title=\"王树义老师公众号\">王树义老师</footnote>和<footnote data-note=\"江sir爱数码\" data-title=\"B站up\">江sir视频</footnote>的引路，发现了<kbd>roam/css</kbd>大法。原来roam是支持代码嵌入的，也就是JS和CSS这种代码块，是可以直接在笔记系统中生效的。那我们就可以用CSS代码开发自己的笔记UI系统了。</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span><span>具体方法</span></span>","level":3},"common":{}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"ordered","items":[{"content":"<span><span>在roam里添加<kbd>roam/css</kbd>页面, 在此页面中添加CSS片段</span></span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"方法一：可以直接写CSS片段，在片段语言中选择CSS，就可以直接生效","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<span><span>方法二：或者可以将CSS片段、变量保存在github上，并用@import语法拉入本地的CSS代码片段。这种比较推荐，因为有很多大神已经做好设计了，我们直接将它们拿回来用就好了，不必自己全盘造轮子（主要是懒）</span></span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>对于白嫖本地端的白嫖党来说，第二种方式很重要。因为<mark>网上大神的方案一般是适配web端的，拉到本地端用有些主题效果就变样了，需要自己调整适配一下。</mark>这样就可以将方法一、二结合起来，先用github的远程CSS片段，自己再对其中的变量进行修改，就能得到自己需要的效果了。</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>比如，我很喜欢的Bear主题，可以使用以下片段拉入本地端渲染主题：</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span><code>@import url('https://rcvd.github.io/roam-css-system/themes/bear.css');</code></span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"header","data":{"level":3,"content":"Github项目地址:&nbsp;"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<a href=\"https://github.com/rcvd/roam-css-system\">https://github.com/rcvd/roam-css-system</a>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>其中<kbd>Bear</kbd>这个主题非常漂亮，美中不足的是，一些字体在本地端显示得太小了，阅读起来很吃力。我们在原主题的基础上，抓取部分片段、变量，对其进行本地端的优化适配。</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>可以使用开发者工具（快捷键:&nbsp;<kbd>ctrl+shift+i</kbd>）来进行定位，找到影响UI效果的变量。</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><span>在<code></code>:root {}<code></code>内进行添加修改</span></span>"},"common":{}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"<span><span>全局字体和字体大小的调整</span></span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<span><span>页面标题</span></span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<span><span>基础文本</span></span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<span><span>二级、三级标题</span></span>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span><span>最终的roam/css代码:</span></span>","level":3},"common":{}},{"key":"code","data":{"lang":"","lines":["<span class=\"be-code__meta\">@​import url(<span class=\"be-code__params\"><span class=\"be-code__string\">'https://rcvd.github.io/roam-css-system/themes/bear.css'</span></span>);<span id=\"_ge_bookmark_end_0.6258898313676842\" style=\"display: none; line-height: 0px;\">‍</span>​</span>"]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"code","data":{"lang":"","lines":["<span class=\"be-code__comment\">/*以下为css变量*/</span>","<span class=\"be-code__selector-pseudo\">:root</span> {","  <span class=\"be-code__comment\">/*全局字体和字体大小设置*/</span>","    <span class=\"be-code__attr\">--ff-div</span>: avenir next, avenir,<span class=\"be-code__string\">'Noto Sans SC'</span>, <span class=\"be-code__string\">'Nunito Sans'</span>, segoe ui, helvetica neue, helvetica, Ubuntu, roboto, noto, arial, sans-serif;","    <span class=\"be-code__attr\">--fs-div</span>: <span class=\"be-code__number\">16px</span>;","  <span class=\"be-code__comment\">/*页面标题字体大小，原主题20px，可改为28px*/</span>","      <span class=\"be-code__attr\">--fs-page__title</span>: <span class=\"be-code__number\">28px</span>;","  <span class=\"be-code__comment\">/*基本文本字体大小，原主题1rem*/</span>","      <span class=\"be-code__attr\">--fs-main</span>: <span class=\"be-code__number\">1.06rem</span>;","  <span class=\"be-code__comment\">/*基本文本字体组合，原主题avenir next, avenir, 'Nunito Sans', segoe ui, helvetica neue, helvetica, Ubuntu, roboto, noto, arial, sans-serif*/​</span>","    <span class=\"be-code__attr\">--ff-main</span>: avenir next, avenir, <span class=\"be-code__string\">'Noto Sans SC'</span>, <span class=\"be-code__string\">'Nunito Sans'</span>, segoe ui, helvetica neue, helvetica, Ubuntu, roboto, noto, arial, sans-serif;","    <span class=\"be-code__attr\">--fs-level2</span>: <span class=\"be-code__number\">20px</span>;","    <span class=\"be-code__attr\">--fs-level3</span>: <span class=\"be-code__number\">18px</span>;​","    <span class=\"be-code__attr\">--fs-codeblock__code</span>: <span class=\"be-code__number\">0.85rem</span>;​","    }​"]},"common":{}},{"key":"header","data":{"level":3,"content":"最终优化后的软件效果"},"common":{}},{"key":"image","data":{"image":{"assetName":"1692603783054-image.png","url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Neonity2020/geekeditor/geekeditor_images/2023-8-21/1692603783054-image.png"},"caption":"优化后的软件效果","withCaption":true},"common":{}},{"key":"image","data":{"image":{"assetName":"1692604208724-image.png","url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Neonity2020/geekeditor/geekeditor_images/2023-8-21/1692604208724-image.png"},"caption":"关掉自定义CSS的原版效果","withCaption":true},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"本文使用的编辑软件「极客编辑器」，自制主题「极客红」（受到Bear主题启发设计）"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"点击<a href=\"https://www.geekeditor.com/\">阅读原文</a>，即可体验极客编辑器。"},"common":{}},{"key":"footnote","data":{"items":[{"title":"Roam Research笔记","note":"https://roamresearch.com/"},{"title":"Bear笔记 | 熊掌记","note":